horopito
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Drimys axillaris</i> a small, slender, evergreen tree with aromatic bark. Also called pepper tree.
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
